[30;1m192 | [0m[35m                        # node value clipping.[0m
[30;1m193 | [0m[35m                        left_child_min = right_child_min = parent_record.lower_bound[0m
[30;1m194 | [0m[35m                        left_child_max = right_child_max = parent_record.upper_bound[0m
[30;1m195 | [0m[35m                    elif splitter.monotonic_cst[split.feature] == 1:[0m
